StarFlier::

She flew along side StarStorm.  "Who are SharpClaws and Wolfstien? 
Are they dragons too?" She looked at the ground way below her. "WOW!  
I haven't flown like this in a very long time. I missed it."  She sed 
up, did a few loop to loops, a double back flip and came back along 
side her new friend. "Yeah, this is fun." She did one more back 
flip. "So, how much longer till we find these friends of yours? Where 
were they last seen? Do you think they'll be ok when we find them?"

She was about to start fling circles around StarStorm, when she 
started to cough.  She hacked and coughed. With one large cough, she 
blew a pure plasma fire ball out of her mouth. "Oh boy. Looks like my 
defence mechanisms are coming on line. I wonder why though. They 
haven't been on line for two centuries."
